I think its the Obcessive conpulsave in me, but for some reaion.. Im having a realy hard time tonight. Im not sure what it is really, Kirk and tony, and VIC and every one i usaly hang out with are leaving for a week, that could be it, or it could be the feeling im having of being played for a fool, I dont know, its just tonight i just have this realy bad feeling in my chest that wont go away, like somthing is missing.. or changing. Somthing has me, and it dosnt realy hurt but it does, it not mello, its kind of a jumpy felling, its pulsing in my chest and wont stop, i have been trying to keep my chin up, and keep trucking along, even thoe this hanst been the easeist few months for me. I dont know, i orderd a pizza earler, and, well, it just wasnt satisfing. *shrug* I dont like feeling like this at all, and realy wish i could explane it. It , just is. Like a building, pounding kind of feels like lost, or miising somthin, kind of a felling. 

I, just wish i had some one to goto right now, i think what i realy need to make it go away, is some one to hold me, and tell me they love me, and to let me just fall asleep in there arms, but, i dont have anyone like that..And i rely need it.I did once,...

So, Darren has invited me to move to richmond and be his roomate. It would realy be nice, i need to get out of this house.

But, the unfinished ...what ever it is with the babycakes... I dont want to miss if...ya know..

But, i would also need a new job, and i cant be fucking around with my money, seeing as i have a new car and all.

This is going to require me to think a bit. Mabye ill do some looking and see what jobs are availble up there.
I would be kinda far from everyone, Kirk and tony, arron, amber...ana...and the rest. /ponder

Yeah, i should think about this.

Well what can I say.

I suppose things have been going well. Asked for a raise the other week and the response? lol "your not worth it"

I found that a little insulting.Not only do I do my job, but I do others jobs also AND made the FAQ for the company.No respect, Oh well at least I leaned something in the process.

Not shore what im going to do about school...I feel the need to finish...but I also feel that I need a more speculated coarse and degree than TNCC can offer me.I know im suffocating here at my job...but it pays the bills..and well...It gives me allot of time to work on things and teach myself various programs and ways of doing things.eh...

On another note...meet a girl..she reminds me of a very special someone...and it scares me.
I do find her adorable.

But...she has someone...of coarse...yet..she likes to be close to me.

I should most likely walk away.

I think I have to many walls to let someone in, But lust has always had a grip on me.

ramble ramble.

I see her every Monday night and I must admit its the height of my week. Scary as it is. Even when I try not to seek her out...she finds me. *sighs*.

I'm a silly silly boy.

She is intelligent, pretty and fun to be around. *sighs* I wish I had more time and less restraint to get to know her better, Just when I feel I want to be myself...all I am left with is saying "your so pretty". My eyes defeat me. but its a mute point as I cannot open myself...as it would be bad and that road I will not walk down again.So why is this an issue? Im a fool it seems lol.

She does confuse me, and I already feel I could never trust her.Seems that type is drawn to me, and I to them.

Cant tell you how many times I have wanted to just lay her down on something fluffy and kiss the many inches of flesh.But I always wish to keep what I admire in that way..vicious cycle.

I think I have put myself in a hole, with my past haunting me. I live a very solitary life now...far cry from my past.I think its just easer to deal this way.

Little Johnny watched the science teacher start the experiment with the worms.

Four worms were placed into four separate jars.

The first worm was put into a jar of alcohol.

The second worm was put into a jar of cigarette smoke.

The third worm was put into a jar of sperm.

The fourth worm was put into a jar of soil.

After one day, these were the results:

The first worm in alcohol - dead.

Second worm in cigarette smoke - dead.

Third worm in sperm - dead.

Fourth worm in soil - alive.

So the Science teacher asked the class - "What can you learn from this experiment."

Little Johnny quickly raised his hand and said "As long as you drink, smoke and have sex, you won't have worms."
